<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<center style="width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; background-color: #f4f7f6; padding-bottom: 60px;">
<table class="main" style="margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; border-spacing: 0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;" width="100%">
	
		<tr>
			<td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.mainstreet.org/"><img alt="Main Street America Logo" src="https://nationalmainstreetcenter2.my.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015aJ00000EU9H7&amp;oid=00Dfm000000BWKj&amp;lastMod=1770631915000" style="max-width: 200px; border: 0;" width="200" /></a></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="content" style="padding: 30px 40px; text-align: left;">
			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p>

			<p>Thank you for renewing your membership with Main Street America! We’re excited to bring you another year of valuable resources, learning experiences, and networking opportunities that make your job easier and maximize your impact in your community.</p>

			<p>Please review your membership information below and keep this confirmation for your records.&nbsp;</p>

			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="details-box" style="background-color: #eaf2f5; border: 1px solid #d0e0e8; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;" width="100%">
				
					<tr>
						<td>
						<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="color: #00466a;">Member&nbsp;ID#:</strong>&nbsp;{{{Membership_Transaction__c.Member_Account_Id__c}}}<br />
						<strong style="color: #00466a;">Membership Level:</strong>&nbsp;{{{Membership_Transaction__c.Membership_Level__c}}}<br />
						<strong style="color: #00466a;">Expiration Date:</strong>&nbsp;{{{Membership_Transaction__c.Membership_Term_End_Date__c}}}<br />
						<strong style="color: #00466a;">Amount Paid:</strong> {{{Membership_Transaction__c.OriginalAmount__c}}}<br />
						<br />
						<strong style="color: #00466a;">Primary Account Holder:</strong> {{{Recipient.Name}}}<br />
						{{{Recipient.MailingAddress}}}</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
				
			</table>

			<p><strong>What’s next? &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</p>

			<ul>
				<li>Log into the <a href="https://members.mainstreet.org/">Member Hub</a> to manage your membership, make sure your profile and staff listing are up to date.</li>
				<li>Participate in discussion forums with your peers.</li>
				<li>Visit the <a href="https://mainstreet.org/resources/knowledge-hub">Knowledge Hub</a>, our comprehensive digital library containing a broad range of resources, including our signature Main Street Approach handbooks.</li>
				<li>Take your skills to the next level at the <a href="https://mainstreet.org/resources/main-street-america-academy">Main Street America Academy</a>.</li>
			</ul>
			Questions? Don't hesitate to <a href="https://mainstreet.org/about/contact-us">contact us</a>.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="footer" style="background-color: #333333; color: #bbbbbb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;">
			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Main Street America<br />
			53 W. Jackson Blvd., Suite 350, Chicago, IL 60604</p>

			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><a href="https://members.mainstreet.org/my-account/settings" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">Update Subscription Preferences</a> | <a href="https://mainstreet.org/about/contact-us" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Us</a></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
</center>
</body>
</html>